        dc:description           "FIGURE 21. Uroptychus pilosus Baba, 1981, male, 8.2 mm, off Ulladulla, AM P65626. A, dorsum. B, anterior carapace, right lateral. C, cheliped, proximal right lateral. D, anterior carapace, right dorsal. E, sternum. F, telson. G, maxilliped 3, right lateral. H, crista dentata, right. I, antenna, right ventral. A–C = 3 mm, D–G = 1.5 mm. H–I = 0.8 mm." ;
